## 🔗 **API Endpoints**

### Field Management
```javascript
// POST /custom-fields/fields - Create new field
const response = await fetch('/custom-fields/fields', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        name: 'agent_experience_level',
        label: 'Experience Level',
        field_type: 'select',
        description: 'Select the agent experience level',
        options: [
            { label: 'Beginner', value: 'beginner' },
            { label: 'Intermediate', value: 'intermediate' },
            { label: 'Advanced', value: 'advanced' }
        ],
        validation_rules: { required: true },
        group_id: 1
    })
});

// GET /custom-fields/fields - List all fields
// PUT /custom-fields/fields/{id} - Update field
// DELETE /custom-fields/fields/{id} - Delete field
// GET /custom-fields/fields/{id} - Get field details
```

### Field Groups Management
```javascript
// POST /custom-fields/groups - Create field group
const response = await fetch('/custom-fields/groups', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        name: 'Agent Configuration',
        description: 'Additional configuration fields for agents',
        location: 'agent_form',
        entity_type: 'agent',
        display_rules: {
            show_when: { agent_type: 'conversational' }
        }
    })
});

// GET /custom-fields/groups - List field groups
// PUT /custom-fields/groups/{id} - Update group
// DELETE /custom-fields/groups/{id} - Delete group
```

### Field Values Management
```javascript
// POST /custom-fields/values - Save field values
const response = await fetch('/custom-fields/values', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        entity_type: 'agent',
        entity_id: 5,
        values: [
            { field_id: 1, value: 'intermediate' },
            { field_id: 2, value: 'Customer service, Technical support' }
        ]
    })
});

// GET /custom-fields/values - Get field values for entity
// PUT /custom-fields/values/{id} - Update value
```

